European Investment Bank Lends Bank of Africa 10 Million Euros

-- B y   D r e w   H i n s h a w
-- 
2011-05-18T13:24:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/european-investment-bank-lends-bank-of-africa-10-million-euros.html
The  European Investment Bank  agreed
to lend 10 million euros ($14.2 million) to Mali-based  Bank of
Africa  to support operations in French-speaking parts of West
 Africa , the European bank said in an e-mailed statement.  The loan will help the Bank of Africa expand in  Burkina
Faso ,  Mali ,  Niger ,  Togo ,  Senegal  and  Benin , according to
